Script info: Show albums of an artist

Input parameters:
  name: Name of the artist

---
Get artist info:
  name: ${input.name}
As: ${artist}

---
Connect to: Spotify

Get all:
  url: /artists/${artist.id}/albums?include_groups=album
Sort:
  by: release_date
As: ${albums}

For each:
  ${album} in: ${albums}
  Print: ${album.name} (${album.release_date})
